4️⃣ Required Software

Install the following software:

Python 3.8 or above

Jupyter Notebook or Visual Studio Code

Git (optional for version control)

5️⃣ Required Python Libraries

Install the required libraries using pip:

pip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn flask
Library Purpose
Library	Purpose
pandas	Data manipulation and analysis
numpy	Numerical operations
matplotlib	Data visualization
seaborn	Statistical visualization
scikit-learn	Machine learning algorithms
flask	Web application deployment
6️⃣ Hardware Requirements

Minimum system requirements:

Processor: Intel i3 or above

RAM: 4GB or more

Storage: 2GB free space

7️⃣ Dataset Requirement

Dataset should contain insurance claim information such as:

Policy details

Customer information

Accident details

Claim amount

Fraud label (fraud / not fraud)

Example dataset column:

policy_number
insured_age
incident_type
incident_severity
total_claim_amount
fraud_reported
